Additional Consent for Commercial Use of Product Licensed under CC BY-NC-SA

The owner of this product, distributed under the Creative Commons
Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0) license, hereby grants
the following additional consent #1:

1. Commercial Use.
    Citizens of the Russian Federation are granted the right to use this productvcommercially,
    provided that all the following conditions are met:
        - The commercial organization using this product is owned by a citizen(s) of the
        Russian Federation, who holds more than 50% of the shares or equity of this organization.
        - The citizen(s) of the Russian Federation control(s) the activities of the commercial
        organization using this product.
2. Preservation of License Terms.
    This consent does not waive the remaining conditions of the original CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
    license, including the requirements for attribution, restrictions on commercial use outside
    of the specified conditions, and the requirement to distribute derivative works under the
    same terms.
